   <category name='mobiles'>

      <section name='guard'>

         <para number='1' comment='Guard - password'>
         The guard looks at you and gives a faint smile. "Yes, you have to give me the password or I won't let you enter the arena. And no, the password is not anything as simple as "password". You won't be able to guess it, so don't waste your time trying."
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='arena'>
         "The arena is the main part of the hunt asteroid," the guard says. "It's where the games are held. You can't enter the arena unless you know the password."
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Portal'>
         The guard explains, "The portal leads to the arena, and it is the only way to get there. But I won't let you through without the correct password. There are no exceptions."
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='nomatch'>
         "Nope," says the guard, shaking his head with a sly grin. "That's not the password."
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='Player gives correct password'>
         The guard nods his head and steps aside, allow you to step into the portal. You are transported into the arena...
         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='hello'>
         The guard nods a polite greeting back to you, but otherwise doesn't seem willing to chat. He's only here to let people through to the arena if they give the correct password.
         </para>

      </section>

