   <category name='party'>

      <section name='food'>

         <para number='1' comment='buy food'>
         A droid hands you the special easter food: it's an egg custard pie. The crumbly pastry is rich and buttery, and the wobbly egg filling slithers down your throat, leaving a slight aftertaste of nutmeg. Delicious!
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Throw pie - player'>
         You take one of the egg custard pies but instead of eating it, you throw it into the crowd at random, wondering who it will hit. But before it can land on any of the party guests, a heroic waitdroid jumps up and positions itself so it takes the pie right in the face. Squelch! Skilful use of a napkin on the part of the droid prevents any of the custard from flying off and hitting anyone. What a clever droid!
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Throw pie - roomex'>
         A pie suddenly sails across the room, thrown by %s. You wonder who it will hit, and get ready to duck if necessary. But before it can land on any of the party guests, a heroic waitdroid jumps up and positions itself so it takes the pie right in the face. Squelch! Skilful use of a napkin on the part of the droid prevents any of the custard from flying off and hitting anyone. What a clever droid!
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='Buy drink'>
         A waitdroid hands you a mug of what looks like hot chocolate, with whipped cream on top. It doesn't seem very party-ish, but then you take a swig and realize it's laced with brandy. It tastes wonderful, and the feeling as the warm chocolate and alcohol slide down is marvellous.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='Buy round - player'>
         You instruct a waitdroid to serve a round, and it hands out mugs of what looks like hot chocolate, with whipped cream on top. It doesn't seem very party-ish, but then you take a swig and realize it's laced with brandy. It tastes wonderful, and the feeling as the warm chocolate and alcohol slide down is marvellous.
         </para>

